  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meteorites 3d</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly through space <strong>in a 3D space </strong>while asteroids are hurdling towards you in this empty void</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arcade Nostalgia</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly around and destroy as many meteorites and saucers as you can before losing all your lives!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The smaller the target the larger the points!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combo Meter</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build up your combo meter by destroying targets in quick succession (try and get on the leaderboard for highest combo and score!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Life UP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every 50,000 points you'll get a life up! (max of 5) so if you lose some don't fret!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >W :: Fly</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left Click :: Fire</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Old bouncy footage (:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023210/extras/5fb5dff994d5af1e9d4737abd194d8ac.poster.avif?t=1754756052\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023210/extras/5fb5dff994d5af1e9d4737abd194d8ac.webm?t=1754756052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023210/extras/5fb5dff994d5af1e9d4737abd194d8ac.mp4?t=1754756052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Realise a classic arcade game in full 3D</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy the Game Created By A Single Developer,</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Remember In Space No One Can Hear You Scream...</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meteorites 3d</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly through space <strong>in a 3D space </strong>while asteroids are hurdling towards you in this empty void</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arcade Nostalgia</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly around and destroy as many meteorites and saucers as you can before losing all your lives!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The smaller the target the larger the points!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combo Meter</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build up your combo meter by destroying targets in quick succession (try and get on the leaderboard for highest combo and score!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Life UP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every 50,000 points you'll get a life up! (max of 5) so if you lose some don't fret!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >W :: Fly</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left Click :: Fire</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Old bouncy footage (:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023210/extras/5fb5dff994d5af1e9d4737abd194d8ac.poster.avif?t=1754756052\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023210/extras/5fb5dff994d5af1e9d4737abd194d8ac.webm?t=1754756052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023210/extras/5fb5dff994d5af1e9d4737abd194d8ac.mp4?t=1754756052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Realise a classic arcade game in full 3D</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy t